400
00:22:06,860 --> 00:22:07,740
Listen carefully.

401
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:08,740
I'll tell you the full story.

402
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:09,900
Then,

403
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,140
