through the freeway.

412
00:22:32,100 --> 00:22:33,700
Is it far from here?

413
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:38,180
I don't think so.

414
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:39,740
Why?

415
00:22:40,180 --> 00:22:40,900
